				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Lowa worriedly mutters to herself as she is cleaning up the remains of the Baneites after the fight on the ground floor. She knows she has to do everything she can to hide all the evidence, or she and her son will be killed. She is doing her best to treat it like a math equartion - something to be solved."
